node.text:
This was me … this was the program I was running … it was one based on a deep rooted feeling of shame … and I had no idea it was there .

I went to the gym DAILY worked hard , real HARD yet nothing would happen … nothing would change . Till I realized I had to deal with the underlying EMOTION that was causing the issue … that’s when the weight magically appeared , when the internal happiness  was allowed to BE

Thing is I’m not alone … for this story is also your story , and your story is also mine .

See we all have deep rooted emotions that haven’t been dealt with that lead to programs that stop us from our true potential .

The “ I can’t be successful “ program 
The “ I always find a way to be in debt “ program
The “ I can’t find Love “ program 
The “ Im not worthy “ program 

Im happy to say that we’ve now helped hundreds unravel their limiting programming … by going underneath it … and discovering the underlying emotion that was never dealt with .

You too can deal with it … better yet , you can heal it … and that’s your journey , it’s all of our journey .

To unravel the fear based program and uncover the truth … the Light that lives within each of us .

If you’d like help , and you’re ready to go In and uncover your own limiting program … click the link in my bio and join myself and a couple thousand of your brothers and sisters whom all are ready to AWAKEN their highest potential on Nov 11-13 

I’ll see you there !

node.text:
YOU have the ability to change your life ! It’s inside you ... it always has been since the day you were born .

Yet the traumas of your childhood and past have caused you to forget how incredible you are .

On this weeks episode I interview my brother @johnj.Rios as he shares his EXTRAORDINARY story of transformation . A story of a normal person just like you who was finally ready to begin his Journey to Higher Self 

From healing his body to growing his business the reality is his story is the stuff of movies! Yet it’s also your story ... it’s also possible for You!

Go right now to DannyMorel.com/podcast (link in bio) and listen to this weeks story of hope and transformation !

P.S Please be gracious with the typo :)

node.text:
If you’re going through tough times ... I pray this video brings you hope ... for this is our true story 

Claudia and I were about to have our son @micahmorel7 ... and I had lost EVERYTHING.

I was down to earning $900 a month , was living with my mother with a wife a son and one on the way , Couldn’t afford rent , couldn’t afford ... Food ... nothing .

I was in Mexico trying to build an MLM business when I received her call , they towed away her car at 8 months pregnant ... as she was at the store and I couldn’t do ANYTHING about it 

Talk about ROCK BOTTOM .

Yet we didn’t give up , we kept trying , kept searching within for any ounce of resolve possible ... one year later I even had to borrow $500 to host My sons first birthday 🤦🏻‍♂️

But our belief started paying off ! 

- I was able to start earning enough to afford Our own place 
- Then I was able to pay back creditors
- Then we bought a home 
- Then we built a company based on helping others grow !
- Finally , last November we sold that company and will never have to worry about a car being repossessed again 🙏🏼

I pray this video touches your heart and reminds you to never give up , no matter how tough it gets .

Remember ... everything you need , to fullfill everything you’ve always dreamed of ... has always been inside of you.. since the moment you were born 🙏🏼

Look forward to seeing YOU See in 2 weeks at AWAKEN !!!

P.S @iamclaudialorena4 @micahmorel7 I love you!

You have the power to silence all the noise , and tap into your own inner peace and power .

When you do , you’ll smile more , love more , attract more …. You’ll more easily call in everything you want in your dream life .

That’s the power of Love , that’s the power of PEACE …. That’s the power …. Of YOU 

Share this one with or tag the 3 people you love the most

Viene desde todos lugares en este momento.

Tienes el poder de silenciar todo el ruido y encontrar tu propia paz y poder interior.

Cuando lo hagas, sonreirás más, amarás más, atraerás más ... Llamará más fácilmente a todo lo que quiera en la vida de sus sueños.

Ese es el poder del Amor, ese es el poder de la PAZ ... Ese es el poder ... De ti

Comparte esto o etiqueta a las 3 personas que más amas

node.text:
Drop a 🙌🏼 if you’re proud of YOU for letting GO of what no longer serves you 👇🏼

Part of the awakening and healing process is letting go …. It’s definitely tough , yet so rewarding … 

What’s the toughest thing you’ve had to let go of ? What did you notice after you let go of it ?

When you share , it opens up for others in our community to see they’re not allowing and it allows them to start their healing journey 🙏🏼

Tip : A daily 10 minute meditation where you quiet your mind does WONDERS for your ability to let go and regain your inner peace and power 🙏🏼👊🏼

Deja un 🙌🏼 si estás orgulloso de TI por dejar IR lo que ya no te sirve 👇🏼

Parte del proceso de despertar y sanar es dejar ir a lo que ya no te sirve …. Definitivamente es difícil, pero muy gratificante ...

Consejo: una meditación diaria de 10 minutos en la que calmas tu mente hace MARAVILLAS por tu capacidad para dejar ir y recuperar tu paz interior y tu poder 🙏🏼👊🏼

node.text:
Drop a ❤️ if you believe in the power of LOVE 👇🏼

Claudia and I have been divorced over a year now … our family is closer than it’s EVER been .

I recently took the boys home to California , I knew what our first stop would be : To see their Grandparents 

Why? Well : First I missed them , and I know my boys did as well … and secondly ….

Because they’re my family and always will be ✨

See … I love my kids so to me that means that means I love my ex wife , I LOVE my in laws and ultimately … I love myself 

For ultimately when you’re in relationship with others …. They’re just a mirror for your relationship with yourself .

You can choose to harbor anger , pain , unforgiveness towards another … yet when you look closely , who you’re really hurting is you 🙏🏼

If you want to change your life , get healthier , happier and wealthier …. Maybe it’s time to let go of the energy holding you back from it all .

Maybe it’s time to let go of any unresolved negative emotions with your ex friend , ex partner , ex spouse or ex lover ?

Maybe it’s time you realize they were a perfect part …. Of your perfect journey … yes pain and all .

Maybe it’s time to stop waiting for them to change … and time for YOU to be the example of change your family is waiting for .

For when you heal , when you TRULY heal , those around you heal .

For the energy of love that flows through you … can’t help but flow into the lives of everyone around you 🙏🏼

@dannymorel 

( español en comentarios )

node.text:
Drop a 🙌🏼 if you felt this 👇🏼

You aren’t seperate from what you want, you are actually ONE with it .

The fact that it’s in your thoughts proves it … as if it wasn’t meant for you … it simply wouldn’t be desired by it .

You’re not even waiting for it , or waiting for the Universe to bring it to you… for you aren’t seperate from the Universe … you ARE a part of it .

You’re simply on a journey , your own unique journey and it’s beautiful and perfectly created for YOU to slowly remove all that keeps you from experiencing Your Highest self .

See it …. Feel it …. Act upon it … BE IT…. Receive it :) 

Stay in gratefulness , and let the rest just flow :) 

What are you grateful for today ? Comment with it below :)

Suelta un 🙌🏼 si sentiste esto 👇🏼

 No estás separado de lo que quieres, en realidad eres UNO con eso.

 El hecho de que esté en tus pensamientos lo prueba ... como si no fuera para ti ... simplemente no sería deseado por él.

 Ni siquiera lo estás esperando, o esperando que el Universo te lo traiga ... porque no estás separado del Universo ... ERES parte de él.

Simplemente estás en un viaje, tu propio viaje único y es hermoso y está perfectamente creado para que TÚ elimines lentamente todo lo que te impide experimentar Tu Yo Superior.

 Míralo …. Sentirlo …. SEA…. Recíbelo :)

 Mantente agradecido y deja que el resto fluya :)

 ¿De qué estás agradecido hoy?  Comenta con él a continuación :)
